    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Devices used to crush rock, usually in the context of the mining industry, either to extract ore or simply to break material into smaller pieces.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
